  "texts": [
    "It also highlights the importance of enhancing keyword extraction and optimizing the speech environment to improve the overall hit rate for case retrieval.Summarizing the results of R1 to R3 from the perspective of the research design in Fig. 13, it is clear that Δ 1 demon- strates a high amplification rate, and the overall performance of the proposed method is sufficient when the influence of r 1 is excluded.",
    "However, for r 2, it was found that the influence of r 1 causes deficiencies, indicating room for improvement.",
    "The loss of intent in r 2 also affects Δ 4.",
    "Nevertheless, if these deficiencies can be prevented, successful keyword extraction and the provision of rich case examples can be achieved.",
    "Additionally, there is a possibility that the influence of r 1 could accumulate across the different Δ j stages, highlighting the need to establish an environment that accurately captures colloquial content."
  ]
}